data.meta_description: en.wikipedia.org Wiki Dalida - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Dalida (17 January 1933 - 3 May 1987) was a world-famous singer and actress born in Egypt with Italian origins but naturalised French with the name Yolanda Gigliotti. She received 55 gold records and was the first singer to receive a diamond disc. An iconic image as a combined madonna, diva, tragic and renowned singer.
